{"TopicId":175595,"ForumId":69,"TopicTitle":"Flags fall down","CreatedByName":"Hotel26","CreatedById":139095,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-04T02:51:08Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Hotel26","CreatedById":139095,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-04T02:51:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is not (yet) a Technical Support question.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHas anyone else noticed that flags can fall down?\u00A0 You place them, go away and, sometimes, when you return, they are sagging, swaying and then they gently fall down.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is not a case of a side-swipe by a clumsy rover driver, nor jet blast from a departing cargo plane.\u00A0 They just seem to occasionally fall down by themselves.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI mainly want to know for starters whether anyone else has observed this and puzzled about it.\u00A0 Better yet, if anyone knows some mysterious cause/cure.\u00A0 (Not a big deal, though.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-06-04T02:51:36Z\u0022 title=\u002206/04/2018 02:51  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EJune 4, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Hotel26\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-04T02:58:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFeature?\u00A0 Even the real ones aren\u0027t all standing up.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.hq.nasa.gov/alsj/ApolloFlags-Condition.html\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.hq.nasa.gov/alsj/ApolloFlags-Condition.html\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klesh","CreatedById":110814,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-04T02:58:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey\u0027ve definitely done that in the past, especially around a scene loading.\u00A0 I haven\u0027t seen it in awhile.\u00A0 What version are you seeing it in?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Hotel26","CreatedById":139095,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-04T03:00:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223392323\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022175595\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221528081136\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110814\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022klesh\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, klesh said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat version are you seeing it in?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1.3.1.\u00A0 And, yes, it\u0027s always after scene-loading.\u00A0 (Thank you for the clue.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-06-04T03:01:12Z\u0022 title=\u002206/04/2018 03:01  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EJune 4, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Hotel26\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klesh","CreatedById":110814,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-04T03:05:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere are two entries in the bugtracker for the flags falling down issue from 2 years and one year ago, from the 1.1.x era.\u00A0 Both only ever got to 10% completion.\u00A0 Must not be a development priority?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nhttps://bugs.kerbalspaceprogram.com/issues/10050\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nhttps://bugs.kerbalspaceprogram.com/issues/9368\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Triop","CreatedById":145841,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-05T01:24:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo idea what you are talking about . . .\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/3BvAGGC.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u00223BvAGGC.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Triop","CreatedById":145841,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-06T19:23:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou jinxed me bro \u003Cimg alt=\u0022\u0026amp;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_cool.png\u0022 title=\u0022\u0026amp;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/bLq5rhN.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022bLq5rhN.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Athen","CreatedById":189381,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-07-24T02:29:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think you need to train you kerbals how to stick a flag in better.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ho Lam Kerman","CreatedById":188455,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-07-24T05:22:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI once had a flag fall, roll and then EXPLODE. (It was a version change, so that could be expected.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mahnarch","CreatedById":114432,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-07-24T06:34:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou didn\u0027t know the flagpoles are actually long sticks of dynamite?!\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"EpicSpaceTroll139","CreatedById":162839,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-07-24T13:17:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nConsidering flags are considered as parts with 0 mass, I\u0027m honestly surprised they don\u0027t do weird stuff more often.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-07-24T17:07:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis does seem to be a support issue. And so, moved to support.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klesh","CreatedById":110814,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-08-05T13:59:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223394369\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022175595\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221528313039\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022145841\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Triop\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 6/6/2018 at 3:23 PM, Triop said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou jinxed me bro\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHigh five from another Orange 2-striper.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}